<node id="CSCE 670 Web Search Concepts And Models">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Web Search Concepts And Models</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">This topic in CSCE 670 covers key concepts for web search, such as text indexing, retrieval models, evaluation, Web crawling, link-based algorithms (e.g., PageRank), and learning to rank.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-467fa41688e2d0b08f251e4c3b54fe08</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774752929</data>
  <data key="d6" />
</node>
<node id="CSCE 670 Recommender Systems Concepts And Models">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Recommender Systems Concepts And Models</data>
  <data key="d1">coursetopic</data>
  <data key="d2">This topic in CSCE 670 covers key concepts for recommender systems, such as collaborative filtering, matrix factorization, evaluation, and implicit recommendation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-467fa41688e2d0b08f251e4c3b54fe08</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774752929</data>
